data.description: **** This property qualifies for $10,000 towards down payment and closing costs.  Please contact me for more information.**** Welcome to 625 S Mildred! 3 bed 1 1/2 bath.  This unique property located in historic downtown Charles Town is situated on a corner lot over looking Jefferson Memorial Park and the Blue Ridge Mountain Chain.  Explore everything the area has to offer with walking distance to downtown, restaurants and shopping, and the Jefferson Memorial Park  trail steps from your front door.   Take in views of the rolling green hills of the park through the 12' by 10' bay window set by the fire place in the living room. This home has a fully enclosed, climate controlled sun porch that can be used as a dining area, sun porch, or den.   Its half finished basement can double as additional living space or a private sleeping quarters for guests or in-laws.  Basement features luxury vinyl plank flooring and built-ins,  with a private entry from the outside.  Built on carport provides excellent protection for you vehicles.  2 car drive.  2 year old HVAC system for cooling.  Tons of potential to make this amazing space yours!
